## Obsidian Essentials

| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| `Cmd+O` | Quick Switch — jump to any note |
| `Cmd+T` | Insert Template |
| `Cmd+G` | Graph View |
| `Cmd+N` | New note |
| `Cmd+Shift+F` | Search across all notes |
| `[[double brackets]]` | Create a link to another note |

